cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image and video stylization using deep encoder-decoder networks. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with real-time stylization of videos. 
3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with image stylization and proposes a new approach for capturing the subtle nature of a style. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new approach for style transfer using a style-aware content loss. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper uses deep encoder-decoder networks for real-time stylization and proposes a quantitative measure for evaluating the quality of stylized images.
